### log in 

POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "folke@wp.pl",
  "password": "test123"
}


### generate TEAM

POST http://localhost:3000/team/generate HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Team 4",
  "numberOfRiders": 12,
  "nationality": "POL"
}

### POST start the race

