### POST /race/:id/segments — append segments to a PENDING race

POST http://localhost:3000/race/RACE_ID_HERE/segments HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "segments": [
    { "distance": 40, "type": "flat",    "gradient": 0   },
    { "distance": 15, "type": "climb",   "gradient": 6   },
    { "distance":  5, "type": "descent", "gradient": -4  }
  ]
}

### GET /race

GET http://localhost:3000/race HTTP/1.1

### POST /race/:id/simulate run the simulation

POST http://localhost:3000/race/99685752-fc51-484c-81e9-3c8cd0e51cdd/simulate HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### leaderboard

GET http://localhost:3000/race/33f42b94-8ad4-47d1-a927-42546acabc81/leaderboard HTTP/1.1
